title: 安田記念の後に・負けてばばんばー

text_block_list.text: Ikuno Dictus, who had been perfectly prepared, defeated Matikanetannhauser.
While showing her frustration, she looks forward... and receives happy words from Ikuno Dictus: 'Because you were there, I didn't let my guard down.'
After that, the two visited a public bath on Ikuno Dictus's recommendation.
They thoroughly recover from fatigue and want to prepare for the next race!
